OL,4,Cqualified' to lead trip which killed
OL,5,Cfour
OL,7,FThe four victims had been part of a
OL,8,Fstand-up paddleboarding tour,
OL,9,Forganised by former police officer
OL,10,FNerys Bethan Lloyd.
OL,12,FLloyd, 39, from Aberavon, pleaded
OL,13,Fguilty to four counts of gross
OL,14,Fnegligence manslaughter and one
OL,15,Foffence under the Health and Safety at
OL,16,FWork Act when she appeared before
OL,17,FSwansea Crown Court in March.
OL,19,FShe was the owner and sole director of
OL,20,FSalty Dog Co Ltd, which organised the
OL,21,Ftour.
