OL,7,FMark Watson KC, speaking for the
OL,8,Fprosecution, told the court on
OL,9,FTuesday, 22 April, that Lloyd and Mr
OL,10,FO'Dwyer, who helped act as an
OL,11,Finstructor, were "not remotely
OL,12,Fqualified" and that the stretch of
OL,13,Friver had a "real potential for
OL,14,Fdanger".
OL,16,F"Although they had undertaken a course
OL,17,Fearlier in the year, this was a basic,
OL,18,Fentry-level course, which was wholly
OL,19,Funsuited to leading a tour on a river
OL,20,Fin spate with hazards such as a weir,"
OL,21,Fhe said.
