OL,7,FHe said the group had set off shortly
OL,8,Fbefore 9am despite the recent heavy
OL,9,Frain and weather warnings being in
OL,10,Fplace.
OL,12,FMr Watson KC said none of the victims
OL,13,Fwere aware of the weir or how to
OL,14,Fnavigate it.
OL,16,FBecause of the heavy rain, around "two
OL,17,Ftonnes of water" were crossing a one-
OL,18,Fmetre section of the weir every second.
