OL,4,Cqualified' to lead trip which killed
OL,5,Cfour
OL,7,F"It was known to the defendant and
OL,8,FPaul that there was a large weir in
OL,9,Fthe town centre of Haverfordwest which
OL,10,Fspanned the width of the river,
OL,11,Fbecause they had paddled over it in
OL,12,FAugust 2021," Mr Watson said.
OL,14,F"The weir had a narrow fish ramp at
OL,15,Fits centre, which was only slightly
OL,16,Fwider than the width of a paddleboard.
OL,18,F"Save for that ramp, the entire face
OL,19,Fof the weir dropped sharply down to
OL,20,Fthe river below.
