OL,7,F"On the morning of October 30, 2021,
OL,8,Fthis was a drop of approximately 1.3m
OL,9,Fbetween the water levels above and
OL,10,Fbelow the weir."
OL,12,FText messages between the defendant
OL,13,Fand Mr O'Dwyer show he had suggested
OL,14,Fan alternative route in Milford Haven
OL,15,Fbut had been "rebuffed" by Lloyd.
OL,17,FLloyd went ahead of the group and
OL,18,Fsafely made it down the fish ramp.
