OL,7,FWhen the participants followed her,
OL,8,Fthey were swept over the weir, where
OL,9,Fsome became trapped.
OL,11,FMr O'Dwyer, who initially got out of
OL,12,Fthe river safely, re-entered in an
OL,13,Fattempt to rescue the others, but was
OL,14,Fimmediately dragged over the weir.
OL,16,FAll four victims died from drowning.
OL,18,FThe court heard that one woman pulled
OL,19,Fout of the trip at the last minute.
