OL,7,FThe evening before, the woman had a
OL,8,Fconversation with Mr O'Dwyer, where
OL,9,Fshe asked if he was aware of the weir
OL,10,Fin the town.
OL,12,FShe told him that kayakers and
OL,13,Fcanoeists do not go down the weir but
OL,14,Fuse a slipway further down.
OL,16,FMr Watson said Mr O'Dwyer did "not
OL,17,Freally reply to this comment".
