OL,16,Fher a "coward" and a "charlatan".
OL,18,F"The only person Nerys Lloyd cares
OL,19,Fabout is Nerys Lloyd," he said. "You
OL,20,Fhave presented yourself as a stone-
OL,21,Fcold, heartless individual.
